  <p class=3DMsoNormal>The <span class=3DSpellE>Shakturi</span> are an exti=
nct race
  of insectoid aliens that are said to have inhabited the galaxy long ago.<=
/p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>Many ancient myths and legends recount the <span
  class=3DSpellE>Shakturi</span> as fearsome invaders from another galaxy f=
ar
  away. They were cunning and merciless aggressors who successfully conquer=
ed
  most of the galaxy. But when they were on the verge of total victory, they
  suddenly vanished without trace.</p>
  <p class=3DMsoNormal>At least, that&#8217;s what the ancient stories say.
  Others claim that the <span class=3DSpellE>Shakturi</span> never really
  existed, but are instead an invention used to slander all insectoid races=
 as
  cruel and evil.</p>
